@bercinho :

`does the Peer eventually communicate with the CA?` :  No - the peer does not communicate with the fabric-ca (or any CA) at all

`The Peer no longer enrols itself (like it did in 0.6) and currently does not talk to the Fabric CA at all.`: This is correct.  The peer and orderer both support crypto material obtained from the fabric-ca but don't require the use of the fabric-ca (i.e. you can use your own CA, bring your own certs, etc)

